  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game is a tower defense game that I completed alone, and like it to support a lot :)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I've only been learning Unity for a few months, so please include anything you haven't done well</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Why make games?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Because it's a crazy Thursday to eat KFC :)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Because the school has nothing to do now :)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Because this can be my graduation project in the next year :)</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Tower Defense</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build your towers, protect your assets, fend off enemy attacks, and crush them</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3420490/extras/b4e9e3c3f4d13d3c7c71423dff426c1a.avif?t=1740750225\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3420490/extras_big/b4e9e3c3f4d13d3c7c71423dff426c1a.avif?t=1740750225 width=800 height=374 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Shoot</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Buy weapons in the shop and get weapons boxes in the field for more firepower</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3420490/extras/c5a457dceb78632ba8af6fc80f1c0b50.avif?t=1740750225\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3420490/extras_big/c5a457dceb78632ba8af6fc80f1c0b50.avif?t=1740750225 width=800 height=392 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Drive</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use beacons to summon different mechs and destroy different enemies</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3420490/extras/8b9be4768abf85b5bd0ebf44bb05fe00.avif?t=1740750225\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3420490/extras_big/8b9be4768abf85b5bd0ebf44bb05fe00.avif?t=1740750225 width=800 height=374 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game is a tower defense game that I completed alone, and like it to support a lot :)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I've only been learning Unity for a few months, so please include anything you haven't done well</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Why make games?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Because it's a crazy Thursday to eat KFC :)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Because the school has nothing to do now :)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Because this can be my graduation project in the next year :)</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Tower Defense</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build your towers, protect your assets, fend off enemy attacks, and crush them</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3420490/extras/b4e9e3c3f4d13d3c7c71423dff426c1a.avif?t=1740750225\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3420490/extras_big/b4e9e3c3f4d13d3c7c71423dff426c1a.avif?t=1740750225 width=800 height=374 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Shoot</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Buy weapons in the shop and get weapons boxes in the field for more firepower</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3420490/extras/c5a457dceb78632ba8af6fc80f1c0b50.avif?t=1740750225\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3420490/extras_big/c5a457dceb78632ba8af6fc80f1c0b50.avif?t=1740750225 width=800 height=392 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Drive</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use beacons to summon different mechs and destroy different enemies</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3420490/extras/8b9be4768abf85b5bd0ebf44bb05fe00.avif?t=1740750225\" data-big